* @{" Highlight " link highlight} the icon by @{" clicking "link mouse} on it once with the left mouse button.
* Hold down the right mouse button,
* Move the mouse pointer to the ICONS @{" menu " link menu} at the top of the screen.
* Highlight SNAPSHOT and then release the right mouse button.

